Homework3:
shuffle game assignment (array, methods, if statement, loop, recursive method)
int array = {1, 0 ,1}

important: manage to create method for each function (2 classes - blueprint and main class)

----------------------welcome to shuffle game---------------------
guess where the 0 is ?
are you ready to play? y/n

if y:
shuffle the game
pick 1, 2 or 3!
if the answer is not 1, 2 or 3 keep asking the right answer
if good guess:
good guess!
if not good guess:
sorry!!! wrong guess

do you want to try again? y/n
if answer is not y/n keep asking the question

if y:
loop the game
if n:
see you next time!
